{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2117, "height": 2877, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "上西村二道街", "block_bbox": [900, 236, 1347, 304], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上西村，位于仁村乡坻坞村西北，原名西村，当地原有岭东、岭西二村，后岭东村不存在，岭西村也只称西村。二十世纪八十年代，因渑池县南西村乡（今并入果园乡）也有同名的西村，根据民政部门有关地名的要求，以此地在西村乡之北，北为上，故改今名。\n", "block_bbox": [332, 377, 1916, 636], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [158, 741, 240, 1485], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "九", "block_bbox": [175, 2187, 225, 2265], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "上西村乃我杜氏始祖流芳公始迁渑池之地，因当地属于坻坞河川地，故称坻坞西村，先居于西村之后街，而后发展到二道街，再后分迁至前阙，更播迁到各地。上西村现存有杜氏花门楼遗址等，成为杜氏根系之地。\n", "block_bbox": [331, 654, 1914, 846], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "本枝世系为：", "block_bbox": [431, 868, 677, 914], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳公——忠—果——真金—三乐——跃龙—芳—桐——允执—廷玳、廷学、廷佑\n", "block_bbox": [335, 933, 1912, 1053], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9211441278457642, "coordinate": [331.0885009765625, 654.7557373046875, 1914.2293701171875, 846.4002685546875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9211052656173706, "coordinate": [332.76031494140625, 377.53515625, 1916.927734375, 636.8705444335938]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8747255206108093, "coordinate": [335.66058349609375, 