村乃我杜氏始祖流芳公始迁渑池之地，因当地属于坻坞河川地，故称坻坞", "渑池", "西村，先居于西村之后街，而后发展到二道街，再后分迁至前阙，更播迁到各地。上西", "村现存有杜氏花门楼遗址等，成为杜氏根系之地。", "本枝世系为：", "流芳公——忠—果——真金—三乐——跃龙—芳—桐——允执—", "廷玳、廷学、廷佑", "杜氏宗谱", "九"], "rec_scores": [0.9983260035514832, 0.9851303100585938, 0.968333899974823, 0.9752258658409119, 0.9985376596450806, 0.9792512059211731, 0.8708297610282898, 0.9824451804161072, 0.9904558062553406, 0.9968673586845398, 0.8595054745674133, 0.973892092704773, 0.9865521192550659, 0.9793807864189148], "rec_polys": [[[904, 237], [1348, 239], [1348, 308], [904, 306]], [[437, 380], [1915, 380], [1915, 430], [437, 430]], [[344, 448], [1915, 448], [1915, 500], [344, 500]], [[346, 518], [1911, 518], [1911, 571], [346, 571]], [[340, 584], [548, 584], [548, 641], [340, 641]], [[435, 658], [1911, 655], [1912, 706], [435, 709]], [[143, 727], [256, 727], [256, 953], [143, 953]], [[342, 727], [1912, 723], [1913, 777], [342, 781]], [[344, 797], [1253, 794], [1253, 848], [344, 851]], [[434, 866], [704, 862], [705, 918], [435, 922]], [[436, 934], [1876, 932], [1876, 989], [436, 991]], [[343, 1006], [660, 1002], [661, 1054], [343, 1058]], [[150, 1050], [252, 1050], [252, 1492], [150, 1492]], [[165, 2180], [235, 2180], [235, 2277], [165, 2277]]], "rec_boxes": [[904, 237, 1348, 308], [437, 380, 1915, 430], [344, 448, 1915, 500], [346, 518, 1911, 571], [340, 584, 548, 641], [435, 655, 1912, 709], [143, 727, 256, 953], [342, 723, 1913, 781], [344, 794, 1253, 851], [434, 862, 705, 922], [436, 932, 1876, 991], [343, 1002, 661, 1058], [150, 1050, 252, 1492], [165, 2180, 235, 2277]]}}, "markdown": {"text": "## 上西村二道街\n\n上西村，位于仁村乡坻坞村西北，原名西村，当地原有岭东、岭西二村，后岭东村不存在，岭西村也只称西村。二十世纪八十年代，因渑池县南西村乡（今并入果园乡）也有同名的西村，根据民政部门有关地名的要求，以此地在西村乡之北，北为上，故改今名。\n\n\n\n## 渑池杜氏宗谱\n\n九\n\n上西村乃我杜氏始祖流芳公始迁渑池之地，因当地属于坻坞河川地，故称坻坞西村，先居于西村之后街，而后发展到二道街，再后分迁至前阙，更播迁到各地。上西村现存有杜氏花门楼遗址等，成为杜氏根系之地。\n\n\n\n本枝世系为：\n\n流芳公——忠—果——真金—三乐——跃龙—芳—桐——允执—廷玳、廷学、廷佑\n\n", "isStart": false, "isEnd": true, "images": {}}, "outputImages": {"layout_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//4fce12e2-dcd9-4f6b-9fa1-73fe71a7c512/layout_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A29Z%2F-1%2F%2Fd33119b94c12a6fb34a0cde2b438e7c5481ef51f959cb9ca0eec305890bc9efc", "region_det_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//4fce12e2-dcd9-4f6b-9fa1-73fe71a7c512/region_det_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A30Z%2F-1%2F%2F1d5c48c44bfc11324703b8fc5427e66fac278610908ca86c7a3ba241dddcc69e", "overall_ocr_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//4fce12e2-dcd9-4f6b-9fa1-73fe71a7c512/overall_ocr_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A30Z%2F-1%2F%2Fccd746cef951a976363b5e6a5811815b329e0a120ba021572205f00ec0b3d888", "layout_order_res": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//4fce12e2-dcd9-4f6b-9fa1-73fe71a7c512/layout_order_res_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A30Z%2F-1%2F%2F1bf25d1972301296726d064c41cff0476eab9b79f6572df27a4eb9e9ac77370f"}, "inputImage": "https://pplines-online.bj.bcebos.com/deploy/official/paddleocr/structure-v3-online//4fce12e2-dcd9-4f6b-9fa1-73fe71a7c512/input_img_0.jpg?authorization=bce-auth-v1%2FALTAKDN8mY5KlNI7zaRpLmOqrw%2F2026-06-19T02%3A47%3A29Z%2F-1%2F%2F57878545591b4d31fa8c303a9357714889e15a5678b28f521341a2e7bef399d6"}], "dataInfo": {"width": 2117, "height": 2877, "type": "image"}, "ocrResults": [{"prunedResult": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[904, 237], [1348, 239], [1348, 308], [904, 306]], [[437, 380], [1915, 380], [1915, 430], [437, 430]], [[344, 448], [1915, 448], [1915, 500], [344, 500]], [[346, 518], [1911, 518], [1911, 571], [346, 571]], [[340, 584], [548, 584], [548, 641], [340, 641]], 